<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397149' id='t-397149'>But in my research, I'm not
interested in looking backward.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400165' id='t-400165'>My colleagues and I in Curaçao
are interested in looking forward</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='403250' id='t-403250'>at what might be.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404631' id='t-404631'>And we have the tiniest reason
to be optimistic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408824' id='t-408824'>Because even in some of these reefs</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410625' id='t-410625'>that we probably could have
written off long ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='414298' id='t-414298'>we sometimes see baby corals
arrive and survive anyway.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419193' id='t-419193'>And we're starting to think
