<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504985' id='t-504985'>from surfaces where corals had settled.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507101' id='t-507101'>And I tried those one by one by one,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509958' id='t-509958'>looking for the bacteria that would
