<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517922' id='t-517922'>that will reliably cause corals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519455' id='t-519455'>to go through that settlement
and attachment process.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522448' id='t-522448'>So as we speak,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523671' id='t-523671'>my colleagues in Curaçao
