<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532074' id='t-532074'>when we put them back underwater.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534304' id='t-534304'>Now in addition to these tools,
we also try to uncover the mysteries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537553' id='t-537553'>of species that are under-studied.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540839' id='t-540839'>This is one of my favorite corals,
and always has been:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544152' id='t-544152'>dendrogyra cylindrus, the pillar coral.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='547073' id='t-547073'>I love it because it makes
