<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='553171' id='t-553171'>and because it's rare.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554635' id='t-554635'>Finding one of these on a reef is a treat.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557695' id='t-557695'>In fact, it's so rare,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558871' id='t-558871'>that last year it was listed
as a threatened species</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561411' id='t-561411'>on the endangered species list.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563290' id='t-563290'>And this was in part because
