<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566621' id='t-566621'>scientists had never found
a baby pillar coral.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570803' id='t-570803'>We weren't even sure
if they could still reproduce,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573241' id='t-573241'>or if they were still reproducing.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='575760' id='t-575760'>So four years ago, we started
following these at night</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578453' id='t-578453'>and watching to see if we could
