<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583992' id='t-583992'>We got some good tips
from our colleagues in Florida,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586704' id='t-586704'>who had seen one in 2007, one in 2008,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590786' id='t-590786'>and eventually we figured out
when they spawn in Curaçao</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593483' id='t-593483'>and we caught it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594866' id='t-594866'>Here's a female on the left
