<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597588' id='t-597588'>about to release them into the seawater.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599532' id='t-599532'>And here's a male
on the right, releasing sperm.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602783' id='t-602783'>We collected this, we got it
back to the lab, we got it to fertilize</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='606491' id='t-606491'>and we got baby pillar corals
