<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622081' id='t-622081'>and settle and attach,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='623757' id='t-623757'>and turn into metamorphosed corals.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626492' id='t-626492'>So this is the first pillar coral baby
