</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631786' id='t-631786'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637230' id='t-637230'>And I have to say --
if you think baby pandas are cute,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='640428' id='t-640428'>this is cuter.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641690' id='t-641690'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644236' id='t-644236'>So we're starting to figure out
the secrets to this process,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647384' id='t-647384'>the secrets of coral reproduction
