<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664757' id='t-664757'>and work with them more often.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666984' id='t-666984'>But this is still so low-tech.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670260' id='t-670260'>We are limited by the space on our bench,
