</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680105' id='t-680105'>Now, compare that to our other crises</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682622' id='t-682622'>and our other areas
