<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686265' id='t-686265'>We have advanced medical technology,
we have defense technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689941' id='t-689941'>we have scientific technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691562' id='t-691562'>we even have advanced technology for art.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694012' id='t-694012'>But our technology
