<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708314' id='t-708314'>My mother described being a parent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709995' id='t-709995'>as something that makes your life
far more amazing and far more difficult</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='714230' id='t-714230'>than you could've ever possibly imagined.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716784' id='t-716784'>I've been trying to help corals
